{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Ten years ago, on a Tuesday morning,"},{"time":3000,"text":"I conducted a parachute jump at Fort Bragg, North Carolina."},{"time":6000,"text":"It was a routine training jump, like many more I'd done"},{"time":9000,"text":"since I became a paratrooper"},{"time":11000,"text":"27 years before."},{"time":13000,"text":"We went down to the airfield early"},{"time":15000,"text":"because this is the Army and you always go early."},{"time":18000,"text":"You do some routine refresher training,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and then you go to put on your parachute and a buddy helps you."},{"time":24000,"text":"And you put on the T-10 parachute."},{"time":26000,"text":"And you're very careful how you put the straps,"},{"time":28000,"text":"particularly the leg straps because they go between your legs."},{"time":30000,"text":"And then you put on your reserve, and then you put on your heavy rucksack."},{"time":33000,"text":"And then a jumpmaster comes,"},{"time":35000,"text":"and he's an experienced NCO in parachute operations."},{"time":38000,"text":"He checks you out, he grabs your adjusting straps"},{"time":41000,"text":"and he tightens everything"},{"time":43000,"text":"so that your chest is crushed,"},{"time":45000,"text":"your shoulders are crushed down,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and, of course, he's tightened so your voice goes up a couple octaves as well."},{"time":52000,"text":"Then you sit down, and you wait a little while,"},{"time":54000,"text":"because this is the Army."},{"time":56000,"text":"Then you load the aircraft, and then you stand up and you get on,"},{"time":59000,"text":"and you kind of lumber to the aircraft like this, in a line of people,"},{"time":62000,"text":"and you sit down on canvas seats on either side of the aircraft."},{"time":64000,"text":"And you wait a little bit longer,"},{"time":66000,"text":"because this is the Air Force teaching the Army how to wait."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"Then you take off."},{"time":73000,"text":"And it's painful enough now --"},{"time":75000,"text":"and I think it's designed this way --"},{"time":77000,"text":"it's painful enough so you want to jump."},{"time":79000,"text":"You didn't really want to jump, but you want out."},{"time":81000,"text":"So you get in the aircraft, you're flying along,"},{"time":84000,"text":"and at 20 minutes out, these jumpmasters start giving you commands."},{"time":86000,"text":"They give 20 minutes -- that's a time warning."},{"time":88000,"text":"You sit there, OK."},{"time":90000,"text":"Then they give you 10 minutes."},{"time":92000,"text":"And of course, you're responding with all of these."},{"time":94000,"text":"And that's to boost everybody's confidence, to show that you're not scared."},{"time":97000,"text":"Then they give you, \"Get ready.\""},{"time":99000,"text":"Then they go, \"Outboard personnel, stand up.\""},{"time":102000,"text":"If you're an outboard personnel, now you stand up."},{"time":105000,"text":"If you're an inboard personnel, stand up."},{"time":107000,"text":"And then you hook up, and you hook up your static line."},{"time":110000,"text":"And at that point, you think, \"Hey, guess what?"},{"time":112000,"text":"I'm probably going to jump."},{"time":114000,"text":"There's no way to get out of this at this point.\""},{"time":116000,"text":"You go through some additional checks, and then they open the door."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119000,"text":"And this was that Tuesday morning in September,"},{"time":122000,"text":"and it was pretty nice outside."},{"time":124000,"text":"So nice air comes flowing in."},{"time":127000,"text":"The jumpmasters start to check the door."},{"time":129000,"text":"And then when it's time to go,"},{"time":131000,"text":"a green light goes and the jumpmaster goes, \"Go.\""},{"time":133000,"text":"The first guy goes, and you're just in line,"},{"time":135000,"text":"and you just kind of lumber to the door."},{"time":137000,"text":"Jump is a misnomer; you fall."},{"time":139000,"text":"You fall outside the door,"},{"time":141000,"text":"you're caught in the slipstream."},{"time":143000,"text":"The first thing you do is lock into a tight body position --"},{"time":146000,"text":"head down in your chest, your arms extended,"},{"time":148000,"text":"put over your reserve parachute."},{"time":151000,"text":"You do that because, 27 years before,"},{"time":154000,"text":"an airborne sergeant had taught me to do that."},{"time":157000,"text":"I have no idea whether it makes any difference,"},{"time":159000,"text":"but he seemed to make sense,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and I wasn't going to test the hypothesis that he'd be wrong."},{"time":165000,"text":"And then you wait for the opening shock"},{"time":167000,"text":"for your parachute to open."},{"time":169000,"text":"If you don't get an opening shock, you don't get a parachute --"},{"time":171000,"text":"you've got a whole new problem set."},{"time":174000,"text":"But typically you do; typically it opens."},{"time":177000,"text":"And of course, if your leg straps aren't set right,"},{"time":180000,"text":"at that point you get another little thrill."},{"time":182000,"text":"Boom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184000,"text":"So then you look around,"},{"time":186000,"text":"you're under a canopy and you say, \"This is good.\""},{"time":188000,"text":"Now you prepare for the inevitable."},{"time":190000,"text":"You are going to hit the ground."},{"time":192000,"text":"You can't delay that much."},{"time":194000,"text":"And you really can't decide where you hit very much,"},{"time":196000,"text":"because they pretend you can steer,"},{"time":198000,"text":"but you're being delivered."},{"time":201000,"text":"So you look around, where you're going to land,"},{"time":203000,"text":"you try to make yourself ready."},{"time":205000,"text":"And then as you get close, you lower your rucksack below you on a lowering line,"},{"time":208000,"text":"so that it's not on you when you land,"},{"time":210000,"text":"and you prepare to do a parachute-landing fall."},{"time":212000,"text":"Now the Army teaches you"},{"time":214000,"text":"to do five points of performance --"},{"time":216000,"text":"the toes of your feet,"},{"time":218000,"text":"your calves, your thighs,"},{"time":220000,"text":"your buttocks and your push-up muscles."},{"time":223000,"text":"It's this elegant little land, twist and roll."},{"time":226000,"text":"And that's not going to hurt."},{"time":228000,"text":"In 30-some years of jumping, I never did one."},{"time":231000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":233000,"text":"I always landed like a watermelon out of a third floor window."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"And as soon as I hit,"},{"time":240000,"text":"the first thing I did is I'd see if I'd broken anything that I needed."},{"time":244000,"text":"I'd shake my head,"},{"time":246000,"text":"and I'd ask myself the eternal question:"},{"time":249000,"text":"\"Why didn't I go into banking?\""},{"time":251000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":253000,"text":"And I'd look around,"},{"time":255000,"text":"and then I'd see another paratrooper,"},{"time":257000,"text":"a young guy or girl,"},{"time":259000,"text":"and they'd have pulled out their M4 carbine"},{"time":261000,"text":"and they'd be picking up their equipment."},{"time":263000,"text":"They'd be doing everything"},{"time":265000,"text":"that we had taught them."},{"time":267000,"text":"And I realized"},{"time":269000,"text":"that, if they had to go into combat,"},{"time":272000,"text":"they would do what we had taught them and they would follow leaders."},{"time":275000,"text":"And I realized that, if they came out of combat,"},{"time":278000,"text":"it would be because we led them well."},{"time":280000,"text":"And I was hooked again on the importance of what I did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"So now I do that Tuesday morning jump,"},{"time":286000,"text":"but it's not any jump --"},{"time":288000,"text":"that was September 11th, 2001."},{"time":292000,"text":"And when we took off from the airfield, America was at peace."},{"time":295000,"text":"When we landed on the drop-zone, everything had changed."},{"time":299000,"text":"And what we thought"},{"time":301000,"text":"about the possibility of those young soldiers going into combat"},{"time":303000,"text":"as being theoretical"},{"time":305000,"text":"was now very, very real --"},{"time":307000,"text":"and leadership seemed important."},{"time":309000,"text":"But things had changed;"},{"time":311000,"text":"I was a 46-year-old brigadier general."},{"time":313000,"text":"I'd been successful,"},{"time":315000,"text":"but things changed so much"},{"time":318000,"text":"that I was going to have to make some significant changes,"},{"time":320000,"text":"and on that morning, I didn't know it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"I was raised with traditional stories of leadership:"},{"time":326000,"text":"Robert E. Lee, John Buford at Gettysburg."},{"time":329000,"text":"And I also was raised"},{"time":331000,"text":"with personal examples of leadership."},{"time":334000,"text":"This was my father in Vietnam."},{"time":337000,"text":"And I was raised to believe"},{"time":339000,"text":"that soldiers were strong and wise"},{"time":341000,"text":"and brave and faithful;"},{"time":343000,"text":"they didn't lie, cheat, steal"},{"time":345000,"text":"or abandon their comrades."},{"time":347000,"text":"And I still believe real leaders are like that."},{"time":354000,"text":"But in my first 25 years of career,"},{"time":356000,"text":"I had a bunch of different experiences."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"One of my first battalion commanders,"},{"time":361000,"text":"I worked in his battalion for 18 months"},{"time":363000,"text":"and the only conversation he ever had with Lt. McChrystal"},{"time":367000,"text":"was at mile 18 of a 25-mile road march,"},{"time":370000,"text":"and he chewed my ass for about 40 seconds."},{"time":372000,"text":"And I'm not sure that was real interaction."},{"time":375000,"text":"But then a couple of years later, when I was a company commander,"},{"time":378000,"text":"I went out to the National Training Center."},{"time":380000,"text":"And we did an operation,"},{"time":382000,"text":"and my company did a dawn attack --"},{"time":384000,"text":"you know, the classic dawn attack:"},{"time":386000,"text":"you prepare all night, move to the line of departure."},{"time":388000,"text":"And I had an armored organization at that point."},{"time":390000,"text":"We move forward, and we get wiped out --"},{"time":392000,"text":"I mean, wiped out immediately."},{"time":394000,"text":"The enemy didn't break a sweat doing it."},{"time":397000,"text":"And after the battle,"},{"time":399000,"text":"they bring this mobile theater and they do what they call an \"after action review\""},{"time":402000,"text":"to teach you what you've done wrong."},{"time":404000,"text":"Sort of leadership by humiliation."},{"time":406000,"text":"They put a big screen up, and they take you through everything:"},{"time":408000,"text":"\"and then you didn't do this, and you didn't do this, etc.\""},{"time":411000,"text":"I walked out feeling as low"},{"time":413000,"text":"as a snake's belly in a wagon rut."},{"time":415000,"text":"And I saw my battalion commander, because I had let him down."},{"time":418000,"text":"And I went up to apologize to him,"},{"time":420000,"text":"and he said, \"Stanley, I thought you did great.\""},{"time":423000,"text":"And in one sentence,"},{"time":425000,"text":"he lifted me, put me back on my feet,"},{"time":428000,"text":"and taught me that leaders can let you fail"},{"time":431000,"text":"and yet not let you be a failure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436000,"text":"When 9/11 came,"},{"time":438000,"text":"46-year-old Brig. Gen. McChrystal sees a whole new world."},{"time":442000,"text":"First, the things that are obvious, that you're familiar with:"},{"time":445000,"text":"the environment changed --"},{"time":447000,"text":"the speed, the scrutiny,"},{"time":449000,"text":"the sensitivity of everything now is so fast,"},{"time":451000,"text":"sometimes it evolves faster"},{"time":453000,"text":"than people have time to really reflect on it."},{"time":455000,"text":"But everything we do"},{"time":457000,"text":"is in a different context."},{"time":460000,"text":"More importantly, the force that I led"},{"time":462000,"text":"was spread over more than 20 countries."},{"time":465000,"text":"And instead of being able to get all the key leaders"},{"time":467000,"text":"for a decision together in a single room"},{"time":469000,"text":"and look them in the eye and build their confidence"},{"time":471000,"text":"and get trust from them,"},{"time":473000,"text":"I'm now leading a force that's dispersed,"},{"time":476000,"text":"and I've got to use other techniques."},{"time":479000,"text":"I've got to use video teleconferences, I've got to use chat,"},{"time":482000,"text":"I've got to use email, I've got to use phone calls --"},{"time":484000,"text":"I've got to use everything I can,"},{"time":487000,"text":"not just for communication,"},{"time":489000,"text":"but for leadership."},{"time":491000,"text":"A 22-year-old individual"},{"time":493000,"text":"operating alone,"},{"time":495000,"text":"thousands of miles from me,"},{"time":497000,"text":"has got to communicate to me with confidence."},{"time":500000,"text":"I have to have trust in them and vice versa."},{"time":503000,"text":"And I also have to build their faith."},{"time":506000,"text":"And that's a new kind of leadership"},{"time":508000,"text":"for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510000,"text":"We had one operation"},{"time":512000,"text":"where we had to coordinate it from multiple locations."},{"time":514000,"text":"An emerging opportunity came --"},{"time":516000,"text":"didn't have time to get everybody together."},{"time":519000,"text":"So we had to get complex intelligence together,"},{"time":522000,"text":"we had to line up the ability to act."},{"time":524000,"text":"It was sensitive, we had to go up the chain of command,"},{"time":527000,"text":"convince them that this was the right thing to do"},{"time":529000,"text":"and do all of this"},{"time":531000,"text":"on electronic medium."},{"time":534000,"text":"We failed."},{"time":537000,"text":"The mission didn't work."},{"time":539000,"text":"And so now what we had to do"},{"time":541000,"text":"is I had to reach out"},{"time":543000,"text":"to try to rebuild the trust of that force,"},{"time":545000,"text":"rebuild their confidence --"},{"time":547000,"text":"me and them, and them and me,"},{"time":549000,"text":"and our seniors and us as a force --"},{"time":552000,"text":"all without the ability to put a hand on a shoulder."},{"time":555000,"text":"Entirely new requirement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"Also, the people had changed."},{"time":562000,"text":"You probably think that the force that I led"},{"time":564000,"text":"was all steely-eyed commandos with big knuckle fists"},{"time":567000,"text":"carrying exotic weapons."},{"time":570000,"text":"In reality,"},{"time":572000,"text":"much of the force I led"},{"time":574000,"text":"looked exactly like you."},{"time":577000,"text":"It was men, women, young, old --"},{"time":580000,"text":"not just from military; from different organizations,"},{"time":583000,"text":"many of them detailed to us just from a handshake."},{"time":586000,"text":"And so instead of giving orders,"},{"time":588000,"text":"you're now building consensus"},{"time":590000,"text":"and you're building a sense of shared purpose."},{"time":594000,"text":"Probably the biggest change"},{"time":596000,"text":"was understanding that the generational difference,"},{"time":599000,"text":"the ages, had changed so much."},{"time":602000,"text":"I went down to be with a Ranger platoon"},{"time":605000,"text":"on an operation in Afghanistan,"},{"time":607000,"text":"and on that operation,"},{"time":609000,"text":"a sergeant in the platoon"},{"time":611000,"text":"had lost about half his arm"},{"time":613000,"text":"throwing a Taliban hand grenade"},{"time":615000,"text":"back at the enemy"},{"time":617000,"text":"after it had landed in his fire team."},{"time":621000,"text":"We talked about the operation,"},{"time":623000,"text":"and then at the end I did what I often do with a force like that."},{"time":626000,"text":"I asked, \"Where were you on 9/11?\""},{"time":630000,"text":"And one young Ranger in the back --"},{"time":632000,"text":"his hair's tousled and his face is red and windblown"},{"time":634000,"text":"from being in combat in the cold Afghan wind --"},{"time":638000,"text":"he said, \"Sir, I was in the sixth grade.\""},{"time":642000,"text":"And it reminded me"},{"time":645000,"text":"that we're operating a force"},{"time":647000,"text":"that must have shared purpose"},{"time":649000,"text":"and shared consciousness,"},{"time":651000,"text":"and yet he has different experiences,"},{"time":653000,"text":"in many cases a different vocabulary,"},{"time":656000,"text":"a completely different skill set"},{"time":658000,"text":"in terms of digital media"},{"time":661000,"text":"than I do and many of the other senior leaders."},{"time":665000,"text":"And yet, we need to have that shared sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"It also produced something"},{"time":672000,"text":"which I call an inversion of expertise,"},{"time":674000,"text":"because we had so many changes at the lower levels"},{"time":677000,"text":"in technology and tactics and whatnot,"},{"time":679000,"text":"that suddenly the things that we grew up doing"},{"time":682000,"text":"wasn't what the force was doing anymore."},{"time":685000,"text":"So how does a leader"},{"time":687000,"text":"stay credible and legitimate"},{"time":689000,"text":"when they haven't done"},{"time":691000,"text":"what the people you're leading are doing?"},{"time":694000,"text":"And it's a brand new leadership challenge."},{"time":696000,"text":"And it forced me to become a lot more transparent,"},{"time":699000,"text":"a lot more willing to listen,"},{"time":701000,"text":"a lot more willing to be reverse-mentored from lower."},{"time":706000,"text":"And yet, again, you're not all in one room."},{"time":710000,"text":"Then another thing."},{"time":712000,"text":"There's an effect on you and on your leaders."},{"time":714000,"text":"There's an impact, it's cumulative."},{"time":717000,"text":"You don't reset, or recharge your battery every time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721000,"text":"I stood in front of a screen one night in Iraq"},{"time":723000,"text":"with one of my senior officers"},{"time":725000,"text":"and we watched a firefight from one of our forces."},{"time":727000,"text":"And I remembered his son was in our force."},{"time":730000,"text":"And I said, \"John, where's your son? And how is he?\""},{"time":733000,"text":"And he said, \"Sir, he's fine. Thanks for asking.\""},{"time":735000,"text":"I said, \"Where is he now?\""},{"time":737000,"text":"And he pointed at the screen, he said, \"He's in that firefight.\""},{"time":740000,"text":"Think about watching your brother, father,"},{"time":743000,"text":"daughter, son, wife"},{"time":746000,"text":"in a firefight in real time"},{"time":748000,"text":"and you can't do anything about it."},{"time":750000,"text":"Think about knowing that over time."},{"time":752000,"text":"And it's a new cumulative pressure on leaders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":754000,"text":"And you have to watch and take care of each other."},{"time":759000,"text":"I probably learned the most about relationships."},{"time":763000,"text":"I learned they are the sinew"},{"time":766000,"text":"which hold the force together."},{"time":768000,"text":"I grew up much of my career in the Ranger regiment."},{"time":771000,"text":"And every morning in the Ranger regiment,"},{"time":773000,"text":"every Ranger -- and there are more than 2,000 of them --"},{"time":775000,"text":"says a six-stanza Ranger creed."},{"time":778000,"text":"You may know one line of it, it says,"},{"time":780000,"text":"\"I'll never leave a fallen comrade to fall into the hands of the enemy.\""},{"time":783000,"text":"And it's not a mindless mantra,"},{"time":785000,"text":"and it's not a poem."},{"time":787000,"text":"It's a promise."},{"time":789000,"text":"Every Ranger promises every other Ranger,"},{"time":791000,"text":"\"No matter what happens, no matter what it costs me,"},{"time":794000,"text":"if you need me, I'm coming.\""},{"time":797000,"text":"And every Ranger gets that same promise"},{"time":799000,"text":"from every other Ranger."},{"time":801000,"text":"Think about it. It's extraordinarily powerful."},{"time":803000,"text":"It's probably more powerful than marriage vows."},{"time":808000,"text":"And they've lived up to it, which gives it special power."},{"time":811000,"text":"And so the organizational relationship that bonds them"},{"time":815000,"text":"is just amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817000,"text":"And I learned personal relationships"},{"time":819000,"text":"were more important than ever."},{"time":821000,"text":"We were in a difficult operation in Afghanistan in 2007,"},{"time":824000,"text":"and an old friend of mine,"},{"time":826000,"text":"that I had spent many years"},{"time":828000,"text":"at various points of my career with --"},{"time":830000,"text":"godfather to one of their kids --"},{"time":833000,"text":"he sent me a note, just in an envelope,"},{"time":836000,"text":"that had a quote from Sherman to Grant"},{"time":838000,"text":"that said, \"I knew if I ever got in a tight spot,"},{"time":841000,"text":"that you would come, if alive.\""},{"time":845000,"text":"And having that kind of relationship, for me,"},{"time":847000,"text":"turned out to be critical at many points in my career."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850000,"text":"And I learned that you have to give that"},{"time":852000,"text":"in this environment,"},{"time":854000,"text":"because it's tough."},{"time":857000,"text":"That was my journey."},{"time":859000,"text":"I hope it's not over."},{"time":861000,"text":"I came to believe"},{"time":863000,"text":"that a leader isn't good because they're right;"},{"time":865000,"text":"they're good because they're willing to learn and to trust."},{"time":870000,"text":"This isn't easy stuff."},{"time":873000,"text":"It's not like that electronic abs machine"},{"time":875000,"text":"where, 15 minutes a month, you get washboard abs."},{"time":877000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":879000,"text":"And it isn't always fair."},{"time":882000,"text":"You can get knocked down,"},{"time":885000,"text":"and it hurts"},{"time":887000,"text":"and it leaves scars."},{"time":890000,"text":"But if you're a leader,"},{"time":892000,"text":"the people you've counted on"},{"time":895000,"text":"will help you up."},{"time":897000,"text":"And if you're a leader,"},{"time":900000,"text":"the people who count on you need you on your feet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":903000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":905000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}